text: Szpak is a surname. It may refer to: *Damian Szpak (born 1993), Polish footballer *Michał Szpak (born 1990), Polish singer *Robert Szpak (born 1989), Polish athlete, who specialises in the javelin throw ==See also== *LWD Szpak, Polish utility aircraft of 1945, the first Polish aircraft designed after World War II and built in a short series
title: Szpak
